== 历史 ==
2003年发布首个公开版本3.12。<ref>{{Cite web|title=WayBackMachine: AndreaMosaic|url=http://andreaplanet.com/andreamosaic/|accessdate=2016-07-03|date=2003-07-02|publisher=web.archive.org|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030702122443/http://andreaplanet.com/andreamosaic/|archivedate=2003-07-02|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=How-To: Make your own photo mosaics|url=https://www.engadget.com/2004/10/19/how-to-make-your-own-photo-mosaics/|accessdate=2008-10-12|date=2004-10-19|publisher=engadget|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081006134825/http://www.engadget.com/2004/10/19/how-to-make-your-own-photo-mosaics/|archivedate=2008-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>接下来的几年中，每年都有一到两次添加新功能。2008年9月，3.3版的[[软件测试|Beta测试]]中推出全新界面。 <ref name="RevisionHistory">{{Cite web|title=Andrew Mosaic download and history|url=http://www.andreaplanet.com/andreamosaic/download/|accessdate=2008-12-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081207121520/http://www.andreaplanet.com/andreamosaic/download/|archivedate=2008-12-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 功能 ==
AndreaMosaic包括许多创建照片蒙太奇的相关功能<ref name="Gadget">{{Cite web|title=Gadget Guy Review: Andrea Mosaic|url=http://www.channel3000.com/technology/14697599/detail.html|accessdate=2008-10-12|date=2007-11-26|publisher=WISCTV/Channel 3000|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081024223757/http://www.channel3000.com/technology/14697599/detail.html|archivedate=2008-10-24|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="PCWorld1">{{Cite web|title=Make Artistic Mosaics With Your Photos|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/146559/make_artistic_mosaics_with_your_photos.html|accessdate=2008-10-13|date=2008-06-09|publisher=PCWorld|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081006024816/http://www.pcworld.com/article/146559/make_artistic_mosaics_with_your_photos.html|archivedate=2008-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<ref name="PCWorld2">{{Cite web|title=Editor's Review of AndreaMosaic|url=http://www.pcworld.com/downloads/file/fid,71424-order,4-page,1/description.html|accessdate=2008-10-12|date=2008-05-28|publisher=PCWorld|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081024233930/http://www.pcworld.com/downloads/file/fid%2C71424-order%2C4-page%2C1/description.html|archivedate=24 October 2008}}</ref><ref name="PCMag">{{Cite web|title=Video Clip — Create a Photo Mosaic|url=https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2192496,00.asp|accessdate=2008-10-13|date=2005-10-05|publisher=PC Magazine|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081025050148/http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0%2C2817%2C2192496%2C00.asp|archivedate=2008-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>除相关的标准参数外，还可以使用以下功能：

* 动态创建图像变体
* 自动裁剪图像以适应图块[[長寬比|長寬比]]
* 自动调整色彩
* 避免重复
* 高分辨率蒙太奇（最大十亿像素）

== 版本号 ==
{{As of|June 2009|alt=As of version 3.32}}，AndreaMosaic提供标准版与专业版。两者有相同的功能，但专业版解除了标准版中200[[像素|megapixels]]和30,000个图块的限制。AndreaMosaic支持在[[Windows_98|Windows 98]]、[[Windows_Me|Windows Me]]、[[Windows_NT|Windows NT]]、[[Windows_2000|Windows 2000]]、[[Windows_XP|Windows XP]]、[[Windows_Vista|Windows Vista]]、[[Windows_Server_2003|Windows Server 2003]]上运行，并也支持通过[[Wine|Wine]]在[[MacOS|Mac OS X]]和[[Linux|Linux]]发行版上运行。软件提供标准安装程序与绿色版的压缩文件。免费提供500张示例图像<ref name="Softonic">{{Cite web|title=Create beautiful mosaics from your own pictures|url=http://andreamosaic.en.softonic.com|accessdate=2008-10-12|date=2007-10-25|publisher=Softonic.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919172029/http://andreamosaic.en.softonic.com/|archivedate=2008-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 许可协议 ==
该软件的许可协议允许免费使用该软件，包括商业用途，但它要求每份被发表或印刷的[[相片馬賽克|相片馬賽克]]及衍生作品均应提及AndreaMosaic的贡献。同样，向大量特定受众出版或展示的作品应添加到使用AndreaMosaic创建的艺术品的[http://www.andreaplanet.com/andreamosaic/artworks/ 公开名单] {{Wayback|url=http://www.andreaplanet.com/andreamosaic/artworks/ |date=20200720011429 }}。

== 艺术品 ==
全球范围内使用AndreaMosaic创作了一些艺术品，包括：

* [https://web.archive.org/web/20081022165521/http://www.dac.dk/visEmneside.asp?artikelID=4392 丹麦官方]参加第十一届国际建筑展[[威尼斯双年展|威尼斯双年展]]的巨幅蒙太奇
