eautiful mosaics from your own pictures|url=http://andreamosaic.en.softonic.com|accessdate=2008-10-12|date=2007-10-25|publisher=Softonic.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080919172029/http://andreamosaic.en.softonic.com/|archivedate=19 September 2008}}</ref>用户界面受到了批评，不过它提供了出色的用户指南并产出绝佳的效果。 

